properties.stmtText: PERFORM GAME-LOOP-PARAGRAPH WITH TEST AFTER UNTIL FINISHED-PLAYING
MOVE "Make a move like 'A2'" TO WS-MESSAGE
PERFORM GAME-FRAME-PARAGRAPH WITH TEST AFTER UNTIL GAME-OVER
IF WS-CELL ( WS-ROW , WS-COL ) IS EQUAL TO " "
MOVE WS-PLAYER TO WS-CELL ( WS-ROW , WS-COL )
IF FD-WINMASK ( WS-DETECT-LOOP-COUNT : 1 ) IS EQUAL TO WS-FLAT-GAME-GRID ( WS-DETECT-LOOP-COUNT : 1 ) AND IS EQUAL TO 1
IF NOT MOVE-COMPLETE AND WS-MOVES IS EQUAL TO 8
IF WS-MOVE-OUTCOME IS NOT EQUAL TO "FAIL" AND WS-COL IS GREATER THAN 0 AND WS-COL IS LESS THAN 4 AND WS-CELL ( WS-ROW , WS-COL ) = " "
MOVE WS-PLAYER TO WS-CELL ( WS-ROW , WS-COL )
